Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and helps usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo heads to the palace of the Soul King for training.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 59
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: The students of the Death Weapon Meister Academy must face their fears and conquer their desires in order to save Kid.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 18
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: The identity of the Titans who have been destroying the walls is revealed, but has their treachery been discovered too late to save humanity?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 11
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: A serial slasher is running amok in Ikebukuro, a district of Tokyo, and some suspect that an infamous demon blade known as "Saika" is the weapon being used.
Title: DURARARA: SAIKA ARC, VOL. 3
Author: Ryohgo Narita and Akiyo Satorigi
Contributor: by Ryohgo Narita and Akiyo Satorigi

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: In this latest volume, Naruto stands up to Tobi and the Allied Shinobi Forces battle the Ten-Tailed Beast.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 64
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ciel enters a college cricket tournament to earn an invitation to the exclusive "Midnight Tea Party" hosted by the school's headmaster.
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 16
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Ash Blake attends the Ansullivan Dragonar Academy, where each student rides their own dragon. But Ash's dragon, Eco, is different and can transform into a human girl.
Title: DRAGONAR ACADEMY, VOL. 1
Author: Shiki Mizuchi and Ran

Description: Tomoe reveals that he is dying from a 500-year-old curse. Will Nanami be able to save him?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 14
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: The 104th Training Corps stop for a much-needed respite in Utgard Castle, but their plans to rest are foiled when they discover that the Titans are now attacking at night.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 10
Author: Hajime Isayama
